item.title: [Delta] d claws are null? [Delta]
item.dc:creator: @PLayRooney PLayRooney
item.description:
@PLayRooney wrote:

IF you add your models to your client correctly you’d need to go to your source and Open “item Cfg” and make a spot for your model Such as copy and paste the last one on the item.cfg list then edit it to the main d claw code 8002 and then edit the Prices etc. hold on ill post what you need in item.cfg

item = 8002 Dragon Claws A set of fighting claws 880000000.2105575155 880000000.2105575155 13200000.3495290539 10 40 40 40 0 0 20 20 20 20 50 7 Change item = 8002 to the ID of your d claws on my server 8002 is d claws but you can always edit the prices. 1st big number is price value then sell value then high alch then low alch if i remember ight.
